      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for someone who prioritizes mechanical reliability over cosmetic perfection. The engine and transmission are in good working order, and the car handles predictably on the road. While the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some paint fading on the roof, it remains structurally sound. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a few stains, but all essential electronics and climate controls are fully functional. This is a solid, honest car for anyone needing reliable transportation at an affordable price point.",
