    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. It runs smoothly, looks great, and is totally ready for its next adventure with a new owner! If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that still has tons of life left in it, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message if you want to come see it!",
      "price": 33500.0,
