    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54B32 straight-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system. This unit utilizes a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox delivering power to the rear wheels via a variable M differential lock. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced with steel plates to mitigate chassis fatigue, and the rod bearings have been replaced as preventative maintenance. The suspension retains its original kinematics with upgraded polyurethane bushings for sharpened turn-in response. While the Alpine White finish shows minor road-wear, the powertrain remains in peak operating condition, delivering a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline.",
