    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a fantastic blend of performance, comfort, and long-term reliability. The exterior retains a vibrant finish, and while there are a few minor stone chips on the hood from highway driving, the body panels are straight and free of major dents. Inside, you'll find a smoke-free cabin with plush seating that shows only minimal wear on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every feature, including the high-fidelity audio system, navigation, and heated seats, is fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and delivers consistent power, backed by a comprehensive service history. We recently performed a full multi-point inspection, replaced the air filters, and ensured the tires have plenty of tread remaining. There is a small, superficial scuff on the lower rear bumper, but otherwise, this car is in excellent mechanical shape and ready for the road. It represents a wonderful opportunity for a buyer looking for a dependable, high-quality ride without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
